      "options": {
        "content": "## Missing direct metrics to add if you want this to be reliable\n\nFound in the original dashboard:\n- appliance firmware/info metrics such as `mqa_info`\n- appliance time/uptime metrics such as `mqa_current_datetime_seconds_total`, `mqa_uptime_seconds_total`, `mqa_bootuptime_seconds_total`\n\nNot found there as first-class HA/DR QMGR health signals:\n- `mq_qmgr_health_score`\n- `mq_qmgr_status`\n- `mq_ha_partitioned`\n- `mq_ha_sync_state`\n- `mq_dr_status`\n\nIf you do not already expose those metrics, create them with recording rules or a small exporter that polls appliance CLI / REST.",
